{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"prefers-reduced-motion","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/@media/prefers-reduced-motion","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol></ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/CSS\">CSS</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries#Media_features\">媒体查询特性</a> <strong><code>prefers-reduced-motion</code></strong> 用于检测用户的系统是否被开启了动画减弱功能。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"no-preference\"><code><dfn>no-preference</dfn></code></dt>\n <dd>用户未修改系统动画相关特性。</dd>\n <dt id=\"reduce\"><code><dfn>reduce</dfn></code></dt>\n <dd>这个值意味着用户修改了系统设置，将动画效果最小化，最好所有的不必要的移动都能被移除。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用户偏好","title":"用户偏好","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在火狐中，满足以下条件则 <code>reduce</code> 会生效：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>在&nbsp; GTK/Gnome 中，可以通过 <em>GNOME Tweaks</em> （在“通用”或“外观”菜单中，取决于具体版本）&nbsp;的配置，设置&nbsp;<code>gtk-enable-animations</code> 的值为&nbsp;<code>false</code>。\n\n  <ul>\n   <li>可以在&nbsp;<a href=\"https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/GTK#Configuration\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">GTK 3 的配置文件</a>中的 <code>[Settings]</code> 模块下设置 <code>gtk-enable-animations = false</code>。</li>\n  </ul>\n </li>\n <li>在 Windows 10 中：设置 &gt; 轻松获取 &gt; 显示 &gt; 在 Windows 中显示动画。</li>\n <li>在 Windows 7 中：控制面板 &gt; 轻松获取 &gt; ?是计算机更易于查看 &gt; 关闭不必要动画。</li>\n <li>在 MacOS 中：系统偏好 &gt; 辅助使用 &gt; 显示 &gt;&nbsp;减少运动。</li>\n <li>在 iOS 上：设置 &gt; 通用 &gt; 辅助性 &gt; 减少运动。</li>\n <li>在 Android 9+ 上：设置 &gt; 辅助性 &gt; 移除动画。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的例子将会展示一组令人心烦的动画，不过当你开启了系统的“减少运动”后就能看到动画减弱的效果了。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>animated box<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.animation</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> vibrate 0.3s linear infinite both<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@media</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">prefers-reduced-motion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> reduce<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.animation</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result","title":"Result","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"例子 sample\" id=\"frame_例子\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/@media/prefers-reduced-motion/_sample_.%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/mediaqueries-5/#prefers-reduced-motion","title":"Media Queries Level 5"}],"query":"css.at-rules.media.prefers-reduced-motion"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"css.at-rules.media.prefers-reduced-motion","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/@media/prefers-reduced-motion/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考","title":"参考","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/introduction-reduced-motion-media-query/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">An introduction to the reduced motion media query</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"用户偏好","id":"用户偏好"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参考","id":"参考"}],"summary":"CSS 媒体查询特性 prefers-reduced-motion 用于检测用户的系统是否被开启了动画减弱功能。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"prefers-reduced-motion","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"prefers-reduced-motion","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"prefers-reduced-motion","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"prefers-reduced-motion","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"prefers-reduced-motion","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/css/@media/prefers-reduced-motion","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/css/@media/prefers-reduced-motion/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS（层叠样式表）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/@media","title":"@media"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/@m